value.0: It looks like there's a hole in the half-buried entrance where you can climb into the rest of the pyramid beneath the sands...

Value.value: *This person looks much like the other tomb robbers you've encountered, except that they seem to be severely depressed.* I've been stuck in here for days... I'm starving, and I can't find my friends... I-I don't know what to do.

*This person looks much like the other tomb robbers you've encountered. They don't seem to mind that they've been trapped in here. But they do seem to have something which they quickly hide behind their back.* What are you looking at? I don't have anything for you!

*This person looks much like the other tomb robbers you've encountered. They don't seem to mind that they've been trapped in here, but they seem to be quite injured.* Y-you... You have to help me. I haven't seen anyone for days. Please! I... I think I might die!
